hopobject.body: How much were you paid in your last job? metropharm ltd Conventional farming has diverted agricultural resources to produce cash crops instead of food. Unfortunately, cash crops fail to earn enough money to sustain a dignified living for the Indian peasant. Furthermore, farmers have to set aside a sizable chunk of money to cover the high cost of inputs like fertilizer, pesticide and heavy irrigation. The expenses keep profits down, leading to low income and poor nutrition.
